transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling.

Speaker 2: This is John.

Speaker 1: How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Hey, John.

Speaker 1: No, this is Mike McCracken.

Speaker 2: I just called a minute ago, but it sounded like I could hear you guys talking in the

Speaker 1: background.

Speaker 2: Oh, okay.

Speaker 1: It was like a butt dial or something, but your speaker was on.

Speaker 2: I can help you.

Speaker 1: Can I get your zip code, too, Mike, just so I can pull up your account?

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: 91784.

Speaker 2: Thanks.

Speaker 1: And then what were you looking to get help with on the order?

Speaker 2: Well, I made an order this morning, and I got a call from my bank or a text for a fraud

Speaker 1: alert, and I just want to make sure that everything is legit.

Speaker 2: Oh, yeah.

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: So you're on North First Avenue in Upland?

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: Yeah, everything is legit.

Speaker 1: So what happened, that happens a lot because we're an online telehealth.

Speaker 2: I think it comes with certain risks with these card companies.

Speaker 1: They're worried about it.

Speaker 2: But your order went through successfully.

Speaker 1: You've already been approved for the prescription, actually, too.

Speaker 2: So this morning, after you filled out that health survey, that was approved.

Speaker 1: This will ship out.

Speaker 2: It should ship out on Monday morning.

Speaker 1: Even though our customer service is based in California, our pharmacy is in Kentucky,

Speaker 2: so it's already, what, almost 5 o'clock there.

Speaker 1: But it'll go out Monday, and you'll get a tracking email sent to you.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: My next question is, I think it billed me a little bit too much because when I clicked

Speaker 2: on it, it was $49 with the special, and then I went $29 for the additional.

Speaker 1: And you guys billed me $63, and then the $29.

Speaker 2: Yeah, it should have given you – I see that now, yeah.

Speaker 1: It should have given you the first-time order price, the $49, like you said.

Speaker 2: So I will refund the $14.95 difference there.

Speaker 1: Okay, that'd be awesome.

Speaker 2: I appreciate that.

Speaker 1: Yeah.

Speaker 2: I'm going to take a few days to reflect on your side, but I did that.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I don't know why that happened.

Speaker 2: Like I said, first-time orders, it is on that special pricing.

Speaker 1: So I just checked in for you, though.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: No worries.

Speaker 2: Thank you so much.

Speaker 1: Of course, everyone.

Speaker 2: Have a great weekend.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye, sir.
